Bugs.java
Swarm.java
Bug.java
ImpactZone.java
ImpactZoneContainer.java

By Matthew McNierney
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Java applet that simulates bugs. Bugs are animated and crawl towards the top of the screen.
Double click in the applet window to create a bug. Single click on a bug to delete it.
Animated red circles simulate the impact zone generated by spraying Raid on the bugs.

Demonstrates object-oriented programming and graphics in Java.